{
  "stem": "4361.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if the testing was not positive, I had to put in a little slip and say, this is where it didn't test and put it on a shelf, where a Frenchman-- now, these are the so-called 'volunteer' French workers who volunteered to go and work in Germany, which as one of them said to me-- [SPEAKING FRENCH] 'We were like check pieces--' chess pieces, I mean, I'm sorry-- 'taken from one place to another.' They didn't volunteer.",
      "word_count": 78
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were forced.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were then supposed to fix it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they didn't fix it, either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it was this sort of unspoken sabotage going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And these Frenchmen gave-- we were about six Jewish slave laborers there at a separate table with an [GERMAN] constantly watching over us-- somehow managed every day to slip a piece of bread, a piece of fruit, and if not that, a letter.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when Roosevelt died-- I'll never forget that, April 19, 1945-- I found that out because one of the Frenchmen sent this note saying, Roosevelt died, but do not give up hope.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war is coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't to me personally, but I would pick them and translate and reply.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was to all of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were very decent, very decent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My camp sister worked in another department.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working in this testing department.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She worked in another department, where she had a very difficult job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think when they asked her what was her profession, I don't know what made her say that she was a metal worker, which wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because she graduated a couple of years before me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if anything, she was not a metal worker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think eventually, she became a doctor.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
